    <name>Pantheon Sound Control</name>
    <summary>Pantheon Sound Devices Controller</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
        Pantheon Sound Control is a simple Elementary based volume
        control tool (mixer).In contrast to classic mixer tools this
        one allows you to control both the volume of hardware devices
        and of each playback stream separately. It also allows you to
        redirect a playback stream to another output device without
        interrupting playback.
        </p>
    </description>
    <releases>
        <release version="0.1.4" date="2018-03-02" urgency="medium">
